column4: The bald eagle eats the squirrel.

The lion is round
The bald eagle is red
The bald eagle is blue
The rabbit sees the lion
The squirrel needs the lion
The rabbit eats the squirrel
The lion needs the bald eagle
The bald eagle sees the rabbit
The bald eagle sees the squirrel
The squirrel eats the bald eagle
If something eats the squirrel then it is cold
If something needs the rabbit then it eats the squirrel
If something is round and blue then it eats the squirrel
If something is blue and it eats the lion then it is round

If something is cold and it does not need the bald eagle then the bald eagle eats the lion
If the bald eagle needs the rabbit and the bald eagle eats the squirrel then the bald eagle sees the squirrel
The bald eagle does not eat the squirrel.
